Package cs301.group8.blem

Class Summary
BlemishActivity BlemishActivity is an Android activity that displays the list of existing photos for a specific type of blemish.
BlemishTabActivity BlemishTabActivity class is the activity that is first called upon initiation of the application.
CompareActivity CompareActivity class is an Android activity class that allows the user to view two blemishes at a time, side by side, for comparative reasons.
Dialogs Dialogs class handles the creation of dialogs in our Android app.
ImageActivity ImageActivity class is an Android activity that displays the selected image from the CompareActivity ImageView or from the BlemishActivity ListView.
LoginActivity LoginActivity class is the first Activity seen by the user if there is a password present.
MainActivity MainActivity class is the activity that populates the list of group names.

SearchActivity SearchActivity class is one of the three tabs organized on the BlemishTabActivity main class.
SensorActivity SensorActivity uses the built in light meter of the camera to detect whether enough light is present for a clear photo, or if the flash option should be used.
SettingsActivity SettingsActivity is the activity in which the user can select a variety of settings to customize their app.
SoundReconize SoundRecognize class allows for the user to use voice input to perform search queries.
